                                  announce@otrs.org
                                </entry>
                                <entry>
                                  Low traffic list, in English, for announcements of new OTRS releases and security issues.
                                </entry>
                                <entry>
                                  <ulink url="http://lists.otrs.org/cgi-bin/listinfo/announce">
